5. Создайте основную страницу форума (`index.php`):

```php
<?php
session_start();
require_once 'db.php';

if (!isset($_SESSION['user_id'])) {
    header('Location: login.php');
    exit;
}

if ($_POST) {
    $user_id = $_SESSION['user_id'];
    $title = $_POST['title'];
    $content = $_POST['content'];

    $stmt = $dbh->prepare('INSERT INTO posts (user_id, title, content) VALUES (?, ?, ?)');
    $stmt->execute([$user_id, $title, $content]);

    header('Location: index.php');
    exit;
}

$stmt = $dbh->query('SELECT posts.*, users.username FROM posts JOIN users ON posts.user_id = users.id ORDER BY post_date DESC');
$posts = $stmt->fetchAll(PDO::FETCH_ASSOC);
?>

