  // Calculate difference in height
  int originalHeight = inputContainer.getHeight();
  int newHeight = calculateNewKeyboardHeight(); // replace with your calculation
  int heightDiff = originalHeight - newHeight;

  // Update height and position of inputContainer
  inputContainer.requestLayout();
  inputContainer.setY(inputContainer.getY() + heightDiff);
}
``` 

This should ensure that the keyboard view is properly repositioned when downsized.

